Title: The Delivery
Plot: Mickey and the team find themselves thrust into a daring, daylight heist to retrieve some stolen diamonds which are buried beneath a busy police station, and things look stacked against them when it turns out the jewels belong to a mafia boss who wants them back. Meanwhile, Albert is visited by a figure from his past who brings a shocking revelation.
GuestStars: Hannah Gordon, Shaun Dooley, Claire Goose, Clive Swift
